{"tid":2132834,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】泫雅IG偷放內衣自拍派福利　粉絲：差點錯過了","createTime":"2020-07-30T15:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T05:11:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":32,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"97fd8ccfd5d28b3ea754f01677769308212cf241","tid":2132834,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:17:05.000Z","msg":"韓國「性感小馬」泫雅出名身材好，她亦不吝嗇自己的優點，大方在IG派福利照。早前泫雅擔當國際品牌代言人，示範各款內衣成為焦點，就連女生的購物慾都急升。昨日（29日）泫雅就偷偷再上傳內衣自拍，不少粉絲表示差點就錯過了！<br />\n<br />\n泫雅昨天在IG限時動態上傳數條影片，影片上單穿內衣的她，對着鏡子自拍擺甫士，可見她對自己好身材自信的一面。不過由於限時動態只保留24小時，所以有粉絲表示差點就錯過了。今天泫雅再上傳一張拍攝現場的花絮照，相信她已為品牌拍攝新一輯廣告照，不久粉絲又有機會大飽眼福。"},{"pid":"fedbcecb5b05fa6b46effd86d0d87a2306f6fb14","tid":2132834,"uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":32,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200730/365573928837582848.png/E1FvdI7YBpwq4YB2NyWLGqHr0N7C8UGeVpUut1aVLrc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200730%2F365573928837582848.png%2FE1FvdI7YBpwq4YB2NyWLGqHr0N7C8UGeVpUut1aVLrc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=484691f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200730/365574190084001792.jpeg/vXzHYvLZXkpYuUh_KUoD-V-DHsr1HZaYxfRNWcX0TVk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200730%2F365574190084001792.jpeg%2FvXzHYvLZXkpYuUh_KUoD-V-DHsr1HZaYxfRNWcX0TVk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=626ec0b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baa405c4d7ac3dcc1fe68a1b2d94340c244a7813","tid":2132834,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":46,"score":-38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200730/365575592848003072.png/83vcNDmW--CX20SnvX8ldsgFCkWPiUW8ME7o-zBO6Ps?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200730%2F365575592848003072.png%2F83vcNDmW--CX20Snv